      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "So, which is this latest defection?",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://twitter.com/mattyglesias/status/1327279949569536002?s=21",
        "html": "<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Hey folks, some personal news. <br><br>Co-founding <a href=\"https://twitter.com/voxdotcom?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@voxdotcom</a> with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ezraklein?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ezraklein</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/MelissaBell?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@MelissaBell</a> has been one of the great adventures of my life but after 6+ years on the job I‚Äôve decided it‚Äôs time for me to move on to something new that I‚Äôm really excited about.</p>&mdash; Matthew Yglesias üç¶ (@mattyglesias) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mattyglesias/status/1327279949569536002?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">November 13, 2020</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n",
        "metadata": {
          "url": "https://twitter.com/mattyglesias/status/1327279949569536002",
          "author_name": "Matthew Yglesias üç¶",
          "author_url": "https://twitter.com/mattyglesias",
          "width": 550,
          "height": null,
          "cache_age": "3153600000",
          "provider_name": "Twitter",
          "provider_url": "http://www.twitter.com/",
          "version": "1.0"
        },
        "embedType": "rich"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "I'm calling this one as a Sullivan, and here's why: Yglesias had clearly caused tension at the site he co-founded by signing the ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Harpers",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " letter on free speech earlier in the year. He was called out by a member of staff, who said that his signature on the letter made her feel unsafe:",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "embed",
        "url": "https://twitter.com/emilyvdw/status/1280580388495097856?s=20",
        "html": "<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">I sent a version of this to the editors of Vox. (I have redacted some bits that are internal to Vox and shouldn‚Äôt be aired publicly.) <a href=\"https://t.co/splNNSMivd\">pic.twitter.com/splNNSMivd</a></p>&mdash; Emily VanDerWerff üôã‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è (@emilyvdw) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/emilyvdw/status/1280580388495097856?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 7, 2020</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n",
        "metadata": {
          "url": "https://twitter.com/emilyvdw/status/1280580388495097856",
          "author_name": "Emily VanDerWerff üôã‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è",
          "author_url": "https://twitter.com/emilyvdw",
          "width": 550,
          "height": null,
          "cache_age": "3153600000",
          "provider_name": "Twitter",
          "provider_url": "http://www.twitter.com/",
          "version": "1.0"
        },
        "embedType": "rich"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "While it's impossible to know exactly what happened within the organisation, there was ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "plenty of reporting about the issue",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "https://spectator.us/why-are-vox-writers-so-keen-on-censorship/",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", and the tension was evident in one of Ezra Klein's podcasts when the internal debate over the situationwas mentioned. There was a tone, a stress, to Klein's voice I've never heard before or since on the podcast.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "It's also worth noting that ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "New York Magazine, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "which was Sullivan's former home, is ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
